Text: "It was my dream destination for knowing to culture Asia and for being into\
  \ most populated city of Europe, being chef and cinematography at the same time,\
  \ it was like golden spoon in the hand. The amount of fascination you can get by\
  \ knowing there style of Sunday breakfast is going to blow your mind. Istanbul holds\
  \ its own unique beautiful, it holds full package like Black Sea, old classics mosque,\
  \ Turkish tea,Turkish delights. \u201C even if you have just one day it is sufficient\
  \ to fall in love with this place\u201D"
